speech:
Hi! I didn't understand. I'm here to help with your order. Please say something like 'New Order' to place a new order or 'Track Order' to check on an existing one. 

For new orders, choose items from our menu: 
Butter Chicken
Spaghetti Carbonara
Tacos
Sushi
Pad Thai
French Onion Soup
Pizza
Falafel
Goulash. 

Be sure to specify the quantity for each item, for example, 'One Pizza and two Falafels.' 
What would you like to do?"
